## ğŸ“ About

**Hello Vegan** is a modern, responsive website designed to promote veganism, compassion, and sustainability. Built with semantic HTML5 and advanced CSS3, it demonstrates best practices in web design, accessibility, and project organization.

---

## âœ¨ Features

- Responsive design for all devices
- Modern navigation with dropdown menus
- Modal-based authentication forms (Join/Register)
- Thematic sections: Health, Campaigns, Success Stories
- Custom fonts and imagery
- Accessible color contrast and keyboard navigation
- Social media integration
- SEO-friendly markup

