## âš¡ Setup & Usage

### 1. Clone the Repository

```sh
git clone https://github.com/KajalMishra636/final-HTML-CSS-Project-Organisation--Vegan-.git
cd final-HTML-CSS-Project-Organisation--Vegan-/Phase\ 1/hello\ vegan/vegan
```

### 2. Open Locally

Open `index.html` in your browser, or use VS Code Live Server extension for hot reload.

### 3. Host Online

- Use [GitHub Pages](https://pages.github.com/) for free static hosting.
- Or deploy to Netlify/Vercel for advanced features.

---

## â™¿ Accessibility

- Semantic HTML tags for screen readers
- Sufficient color contrast (WCAG AA)
- Keyboard-friendly navigation and modals
- Alt text for all images
- Responsive layouts for all screen sizes

